sequenceDiagram
title: Compare two genomes(dotplot of Aradu vs. Araca)
    participant u as User
    participant j as JBrowse2 
    u->>j: Choose Dotplot view
    j->>u: Assembly selection  
    u->>j: Ardu.gnm2 and Araca.gnm1
    Note right of j: Matrix view
    u->>j: Zoom(in/out) until two needed Chrs (Chr 5)<br> on x and y axes visible
    u->>j: Select entire rectangle(click-drag) <br>representing the two Chrs for comparison.  
    u->>j: Select zoom in from popup. 
    j->>u: An empty chart appears 
    Note right of j: Track selection(&#9776) <br>(right panel) 
    u->>j: Select aradu.gnm2-x-araca.gnm1
    Note right of j: Dotplot of the selected region <br>or Chr appears
    Note right of u: (Optional) Add synteny view of region
    u->>j: Select a region from dotplot (click-drag)
    Note right of j: Options in Popup
    u->>j: Select open linear synteny view.
    Note right of u: Draws synteny in bottom viewer




